com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.scoreboard

Class ScoreboardCallback

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.scoreboard.ScoreboardCallback
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FrameCallback

    public final class ScoreboardCallback
extends java.lang.Object
implements FrameCallback
    The callback used to update scoreboard for each frame when necessary.

    By default, the scoreboard name will be set to the plugin name plus a space and "Video Player". For example, if your plugin name was called "MyPlugin", the scoreboard which would be used would be named: "MyPlugin Video Player".
